oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fba791f4cf2adb2af034b6ecffce3cd048d48ce","tid":24391,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打去電訊公司整啦 之前我都試過咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我HKBN<br />\n佢話連線正常<br />\n的確我電腦連線都正常</blockquote><br />\n換過個router啦，自己router嘅嘢佢地唔會幫你維修，佢地只係確保直線落電腦係正常就ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我尋晚reset左個router好似好左小小<br />\n可能真係佢問題<br />\n但係點解用電腦又冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為電腦插線 係咪</blockquote><br />\n當然都係wifi fair test <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你屋企人啲電話連個wifi有無你咁嘅問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有"},{"pid":"c3b5941e39461e5ee024b9f9bff162d78e106db9","tid":24391,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打去電訊公司整啦 之前我都試過咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我HKBN<br />\n佢話連線正常<br />\n的確我電腦連線都正常</blockquote><br />\n之前我情況係100m 寬頻 ，電腦上網ok, 但好慢，wifi近乎連唔到咁濟，用3G 275k仲快過佢, 因為果排奥運 想用mytv super睇，初期仲以為係app問題，終於忍唔住打去HKBN,<br />\n佢線路正常，但我上個測速網得12-19m速度，仲叫我開住電腦4小時，夜晚7點俾個report我，仆佢個街 最尾影都冇隻 <br />\n過左日先打黎話線路都係正常 要安排師傅上門。就係上門前一日又打黎，話check到線路固障，已經修復完 . ok的話cancel上門。PK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我請埋假佢先話唔使上門都搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢依家好撚契鳩弟<br />\n上門冇事嘅話收八舊<br />\n真係家爺仔乸玩鳩囇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個同你講要收八舊咁撚好，我做咁耐都未見過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打去叫佢Check<br />\n佢話上左門檢查如果唔係佢地問題要收返檢查費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年上過嚟一次檢查，結果係個盒仔條線斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012018052037764057a4a095bcd8654d49778a3c","tid":24391,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打去電訊公司整啦 之前我都試過咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我HKBN<br />\n佢話連線正常<br />\n的確我電腦連線都正常</blockquote><br />\n換過個router啦，自己router嘅嘢佢地唔會幫你維修，佢地只係確保直線落電腦係正常就ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我尋晚reset左個router好似好左小小<br />\n可能真係佢問題<br />\n但係點解用電腦又冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為電腦插線 係咪</blockquote><br />\n當然都係wifi fair test <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你屋企人啲電話連個wifi有無你咁嘅問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有</blockquote><br />\n咁好大機會係router問題，更何況係tp link"},{"pid":"cfc06aa6b9a67b8127b13f0719c230e625d8c0c0","tid":24391,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:55:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打去電訊公司整啦 之前我都試過咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我HKBN<br />\n佢話連線正常<br />\n的確我電腦連線都正常</blockquote><br />\n換過個router啦，自己router嘅嘢佢地唔會幫你維修，佢地只係確保直線落電腦係正常就ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我尋晚reset左個router好似好左小小<br />\n可能真係佢問題<br />\n但係點解用電腦又冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為電腦插線 係咪</blockquote><br />\n當然都係wifi fair test <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你屋企人啲電話連個wifi有無你咁嘅問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有</blockquote><br />\n咁好大機會係router問題，更何況係tp link</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有理冇理買個新算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n二三百呎左右<br />\n應該係100mb"},{"pid":"b4cc931509f8b0d595bb51563d3ac25e4